1
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:12,264
(Sakuma)

2
00:00:12,289 --> 00:00:15,950
I'll be taking charge of this class
in place of Suzugi-sensei.

3
00:00:15,970 --> 00:00:17,610
I'm Sakuma Takayuki.

4
00:00:18,202 --> 00:00:19,611
Please welcome me well.

5
00:00:24,202 --> 00:00:25,203
Excuse me.

6
00:00:25,380 --> 00:00:26,421
Yes?

7
00:00:26,522 --> 00:00:28,752
There's something on your back.

8
00:00:36,499 --> 00:00:37,516
I see.

9
00:00:38,609 --> 00:00:41,395
Yesterday, my niece came to visit me.

10
00:00:42,846 --> 00:00:44,359
She draws well, doesn't she?

11
00:00:49,016 --> 00:00:51,626
All right then. Let's check the attendance.

12
00:00:52,090 --> 00:00:54,300
(Students List, Sixth Grade Class C)

13
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:55,678
(Sakuma)

14
00:00:55,703 --> 00:00:58,790
I think I mistook
a TV remote controller for my phone.

15
00:01:04,511 --> 00:01:07,281
Still as goofy as ever.

16
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:09,387
(Minato Shouji Coin Laundry)

17
00:01:09,412 --> 00:01:11,302
Minato Shouji Coin Laundry,

18
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:13,370
the laundromat loved by the locals.

19
00:01:13,370 --> 00:01:14,521
(Closed for three days due to personal reasons.
Minato Akira, Owner and Operator)

20
00:01:14,546 --> 00:01:15,560
Currently...

21
00:01:16,193 --> 00:01:17,933
Minato Akira, the owner...

22
00:01:22,716 --> 00:01:24,216
is on a three-day-two-night trip

23
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,400
to heal his heart.

24
00:01:31,930 --> 00:01:33,036
Hello.

25
00:01:33,632 --> 00:01:36,022
It's been a long time, Akira-kun.

26
00:01:37,706 --> 00:01:38,706
At the time,

27
00:01:39,005 --> 00:01:41,095
upon seeing the face of Sakuma-sensei.

28
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,760
Uh, I...

29
00:01:44,860 --> 00:01:46,485
My stomach hurts as well as my head.

30
00:01:47,014 --> 00:01:48,064
Excuse me.

31
00:01:48,094 --> 00:01:49,154
Minato-san.

32
00:01:50,981 --> 00:01:52,571
I ran off just like that.

33
00:01:53,655 --> 00:01:56,195
I'm such a loser.

34
00:02:05,918 --> 00:02:08,220
Minato-san, are you alright?

35
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:10,720
Aren't you feeling well?
Are you at home now?

36
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:13,160
Minato-san, where are you?

37
00:02:13,341 --> 00:02:14,591
I wish to talk to you.

38
00:02:19,408 --> 00:02:20,748
Do I...

39
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:23,490
still like him?

40
00:02:25,613 --> 00:02:28,590
Isn't time supposed to make it any better?

41
00:03:33,370 --> 00:03:34,650
"Minato's Laundromat"

42
00:03:37,416 --> 00:03:38,676
Sakuma-sensei.

43
00:03:46,049 --> 00:03:47,083
What is it?

44
00:03:47,593 --> 00:03:50,159
You're Shintaro-kun.

45
00:03:50,810 --> 00:03:51,854
May I ask...

46
00:03:52,803 --> 00:03:55,408
what you think of Minato-san?

47
00:03:56,130 --> 00:03:57,690
Minato...

48
00:03:58,699 --> 00:03:59,839
You mean Akira-kun?

49
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,720
- What do I think of him?
- I mean...

50
00:04:03,745 --> 00:04:04,815
Shin.

51
00:04:06,268 --> 00:04:08,088
That's too rude of you.

52
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:09,713
I'm sorry, Takayuki-san.

53
00:04:10,379 --> 00:04:11,524
Let's go.

54
00:04:16,890 --> 00:04:20,020
Tell me.
What's between Akira-san and Takayuki-san?

55
00:04:23,876 --> 00:04:25,407
It has nothing to do with you.

56
00:04:28,677 --> 00:04:30,545
Come on, just tell me.

57
00:04:30,570 --> 00:04:33,280
These two hang out together a lot lately.

58
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,341
Yes.

59
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:42,800
(Minato Shouji Coin Laundry)

60
00:04:45,613 --> 00:04:47,754
Why have you been taking so many breaks recently?

61
00:04:47,778 --> 00:04:48,936
What happened?

62
00:04:51,036 --> 00:04:52,256
It's nothing.

63
00:04:55,983 --> 00:04:57,380
Have you...

64
00:05:01,374 --> 00:05:02,574
done it with Shin?

65
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:03,895
Ouch!

66
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:06,144
Gosh.

67
00:05:07,354 --> 00:05:09,810
What nonsense are you talking about?

68
00:05:10,841 --> 00:05:12,376
I already told you.

69
00:05:12,707 --> 00:05:14,888
Shin and I aren't dating.

70
00:05:17,810 --> 00:05:20,453
So Shin's love is still unrequited.

71
00:05:30,283 --> 00:05:31,513
Hey, Akira-san.

72
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:35,238
Don't you like younger guys?

73
00:05:38,490 --> 00:05:39,557
Do you find us too unreliable?

74
00:05:40,350 --> 00:05:41,875
