75
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:44,076
What about me?

76
00:05:44,565 --> 00:05:45,843
What do you think of me?

77
00:05:53,968 --> 00:05:55,104
What's with you?

78
00:05:55,866 --> 00:05:57,142
Are you trying to copy Shin?

79
00:05:57,450 --> 00:05:58,900
Or are you looking for some advice on love?

80
00:06:03,330 --> 00:06:04,362
Listen.

81
00:06:04,909 --> 00:06:07,419
You can be quite frivolous
but you're a good guy.

82
00:06:07,894 --> 00:06:09,623
If you sincerely confess your love,

83
00:06:10,006 --> 00:06:11,752
that person will understand your feelings.

84
00:06:15,927 --> 00:06:16,979
Minato-san.

85
00:06:17,653 --> 00:06:20,333
What are you doing alone with Hanabusa?

86
00:06:21,970 --> 00:06:23,260
Having an affair?

87
00:06:23,290 --> 00:06:25,218
Are you crazy? Stop it.

88
00:06:26,713 --> 00:06:28,521
He was just seeking some advice on love.

89
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,072
Right, Asuka?

90
00:06:30,940 --> 00:06:33,960
Well, if you say so.

91
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:38,832
See you later, Akira-san.

92
00:06:39,253 --> 00:06:40,283
Bye.

93
00:06:49,169 --> 00:06:50,274
What's with you?

94
00:06:51,210 --> 00:06:52,310
Are you mad at me?

95
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:53,580
Yes, I'm mad.

96
00:06:54,421 --> 00:06:57,041
You didn't reply to my texts again.
And you weren't at the laundromat.

97
00:06:57,090 --> 00:06:58,494
I'm sorry.

98
00:06:59,467 --> 00:07:01,431
Can you not make such a scary face?

99
00:07:03,284 --> 00:07:06,246
I just went on a trip for a change of mood.

100
00:07:07,119 --> 00:07:08,134
A trip?

101
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:12,365
It's good to take a break
once in a while, right?

102
00:07:15,850 --> 00:07:17,651
I have a souvenir for you too.

103
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,564
Here.

104
00:07:24,589 --> 00:07:27,104
(Bean Sprout)

105
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:31,384
So? It's cute, isn't it?

106
00:07:36,984 --> 00:07:38,445
Thank you.

107
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:40,727
Come on.

108
00:07:42,718 --> 00:07:44,524
So even that can't cheer you up?

109
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,102
Well, it can't be helped then.

110
00:07:50,330 --> 00:07:51,383
Alright.

111
00:07:51,955 --> 00:07:55,180
I'll treat you
to a watermelon shake the next time.

112
00:07:56,470 --> 00:07:57,577
Watermelon shake?

113
00:07:57,764 --> 00:07:58,866
That's right.

114
00:07:59,460 --> 00:08:02,735
Back in high school, I always had it
on the way back from the club.

115
00:08:03,831 --> 00:08:04,960
It's good, you know.

116
00:08:05,527 --> 00:08:06,871
Let's have it together next time.

117
00:08:09,405 --> 00:08:10,442
Together?

118
00:08:12,090 --> 00:08:13,226
Yes, together.

119
00:08:14,341 --> 00:08:16,327
Yes. Definitely a yes.

120
00:08:16,352 --> 00:08:17,928
I'll hold you to that, Minato-san.

121
00:08:18,264 --> 00:08:19,386
Sure.

122
00:08:19,820 --> 00:08:20,934
I promise.

123
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,169
So it's a date.

124
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,509
No, it's not.

125
00:08:44,350 --> 00:08:45,492
Minato-san.

126
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,210
