127
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:55,835
No matter who it is you like,

128
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:59,070
I still like you.

129
00:09:00,470 --> 00:09:01,550
Besides,

130
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,044
whoever that person is...

131
00:09:04,652 --> 00:09:06,279
I won't be giving up.

132
00:09:15,661 --> 00:09:17,452
I'm glad I got to meet you today.

133
00:09:18,690 --> 00:09:20,170
I'll be off now.

134
00:09:27,951 --> 00:09:29,100
Even though...

135
00:09:29,638 --> 00:09:31,386
he's so straightforward,

136
00:09:35,897 --> 00:09:36,964
But...

137
00:09:39,331 --> 00:09:40,878
nothing has changed for me at all.

138
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:46,519
Damn it.

139
00:09:47,147 --> 00:09:49,944
How much longer am I going to hesitate?

140
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:52,692
Damn it.

141
00:09:54,267 --> 00:09:55,637
It's time I have to...

142
00:09:57,020 --> 00:10:00,310
(Sakuma Store)

143
00:10:00,980 --> 00:10:02,202
Finally...

144
00:10:02,794 --> 00:10:04,435
I'm here.

145
00:10:10,666 --> 00:10:11,882
Hello.

146
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:23,890
Could this be...

147
00:10:24,963 --> 00:10:26,483
Sensei's nephew?

148
00:10:27,115 --> 00:10:28,149
Shuu-kun, right?

149
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,564
You startled me.

150
00:10:31,730 --> 00:10:34,530
I heard you went abroad for a while.

151
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,830
Are you already back?

152
00:10:37,272 --> 00:10:38,304
Want cigarettes?

153
00:10:39,991 --> 00:10:41,014
Uh...

154
00:10:41,460 --> 00:10:43,100
