155
00:10:43,805 --> 00:10:44,983
Sakuma-sensei...

156
00:10:45,743 --> 00:10:46,760
No, I mean...

157
00:10:47,530 --> 00:10:48,848
Where's Takayuki-sensei?

158
00:11:02,997 --> 00:11:04,835
Takayuki lives by himself now.

159
00:11:05,791 --> 00:11:06,819
All right.

160
00:11:13,020 --> 00:11:14,072
Thank you.

161
00:11:14,850 --> 00:11:17,330
(Takayuki)

162
00:11:18,168 --> 00:11:21,619
If I'm to visit him at his personal residence,
it seems a bit...

163
00:11:28,110 --> 00:11:29,840
By the way...

164
00:11:30,791 --> 00:11:33,128
what am I to say when I meet him?

165
00:11:38,245 --> 00:11:40,062
(Katsuki)
You know the new teacher

166
00:11:40,087 --> 00:11:42,830
at the tutorial school is so cool.

167
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:46,980
He's so quiet and aloof
that you can't tell what he's thinking.

168
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,942
But he is even cooler that way.

169
00:11:52,174 --> 00:11:53,767
Hey, Shin.

170
00:11:54,458 --> 00:11:55,587
Sorry, what?

171
00:11:58,350 --> 00:11:59,385
By the way,

172
00:11:59,409 --> 00:12:01,721
aren't you making too many of it?

173
00:12:10,652 --> 00:12:11,685
Shin.

174
00:12:13,045 --> 00:12:14,435
You were supposed to return home by now.

175
00:12:16,131 --> 00:12:17,601
I've brought you some fried mackerel

176
00:12:18,238 --> 00:12:19,410
to thank you for the gift.

177
00:12:20,581 --> 00:12:22,771
You didn't have to.

178
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:27,756
Anyway,

179
00:12:28,381 --> 00:12:29,382
thanks.

180
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,001
Should we eat it together?

181
00:12:58,690 --> 00:13:01,890
(Bean Sprout)

182
00:13:06,590 --> 00:13:08,334
Where have you been today?

183
00:13:09,684 --> 00:13:10,980
Are you all right?

184
00:13:11,190 --> 00:13:12,225
Yes.

185
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:15,020
You dropped something.

186
00:13:17,780 --> 00:13:18,842
Hey, that's...

187
00:13:19,141 --> 00:13:20,281
Takayuki...

188
00:13:22,176 --> 00:13:23,236
This is...

189
00:13:23,486 --> 00:13:25,486
Sakuma-sensei's address.

190
00:13:34,865 --> 00:13:35,897
Well...

191
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:38,670
actually...

192
00:13:40,443 --> 00:13:42,201
I was thinking of meeting Sakuma-sensei.

193
00:13:43,590 --> 00:13:45,158
So I went to his shop.

194
00:13:49,490 --> 00:13:51,094
But I didn't find him there.

195
00:13:52,450 --> 00:13:54,673
It turns out he lives by himself now.

196
00:13:59,490 --> 00:14:00,606
Are you going to meet him?

197
00:14:06,310 --> 00:14:07,341
Well...

198
00:14:09,626 --> 00:14:10,763
Just go.

199
00:14:12,340 --> 00:14:13,519
It's all right.

200
00:14:14,034 --> 00:14:15,588
If something were to ever happen to you,

201
00:14:15,963 --> 00:14:17,729
I'll come and find you immediately.

202
00:14:21,204 --> 00:14:24,163
You're always exaggerating it.

203
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:26,589
All right.

204
00:14:26,878 --> 00:14:28,904
It's not because you told me to.

205
00:14:29,373 --> 00:14:31,214
But I need to settle things once and for all.

206
00:14:32,060 --> 00:14:33,272
I'm going to meet him.

207
00:14:38,210 --> 00:14:39,312
Thank you.

208
00:14:43,888 --> 00:14:45,631
Even when I said it like that...

209
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:49,655
but when I finally arrived at his place,

210
00:14:50,831 --> 00:14:53,390
I felt so nervous that my stomach started hurting.

211
00:14:56,302 --> 00:14:59,194
I'm sorry, Shin. I don't feel good at all.

212
00:14:59,370 --> 00:15:01,063
I should back off for today.

213
00:15:01,436 --> 00:15:02,636
Akira-kun.

214
00:15:11,752 --> 00:15:13,253
Please, have a drink.

215
00:15:14,670 --> 00:15:16,600
I'm sorry for coming over so suddenly.

216
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:18,860
No problem. I'm glad you came.

217
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,393
Are you all right?

218
00:15:27,699 --> 00:15:28,860
I'm all right.

219
00:15:28,971 --> 00:15:30,482
Just a little choke.

220
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,440
Sensei.

221
00:15:36,321 --> 00:15:37,625
You haven't changed one bit.

222
00:15:39,613 --> 00:15:40,661
Oh, right.

223
00:15:40,686 --> 00:15:42,662
I have something to show you too.

224
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:46,679
If I'm not mistaken,
it should be somewhere here.

225
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:49,048
Oh, I found it.

226
00:15:51,730 --> 00:15:52,777
Here.

227
00:15:54,230 --> 00:15:56,269
While you were still in tenth grade,

228
00:15:56,440 --> 00:16:00,026
and I was just hired to teach
at Keyaki High School.

229
00:16:00,810 --> 00:16:01,994
No.

230
00:16:02,503 --> 00:16:04,230
