231
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:05,531
It suited you though.

232
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:08,040
Even if it was against the school rules.

233
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:13,906
I, at the time,...

234
00:16:14,830 --> 00:16:15,942
