238
00:16:21,429 --> 00:16:22,597
Don't you think so, Akira?

239
00:16:23,115 --> 00:16:24,128
Yes.

240
00:16:24,199 --> 00:16:27,529
Right? She's the cutest ever.

241
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,207
I was good for nothing.

242
00:16:32,102 --> 00:16:33,249
I was reckless.

243
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,862
Hello, Akira-kun.

244
00:16:45,703 --> 00:16:46,935
Do you remember me?

245
00:16:47,355 --> 00:16:49,629
I'm Sakuma Takayuki from Sakuma Store.

246
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:51,043
Sakuma Store?

247
00:16:52,263 --> 00:16:55,123
When you were little,
I was often asked to babysit you.

248
00:16:55,483 --> 00:16:57,623
We played together all the time.

249
00:16:58,327 --> 00:16:59,599
I don't remember such a thing.

250
00:17:13,080 --> 00:17:14,183
Hey.

251
00:17:16,813 --> 00:17:18,027
Are you all right?

252
00:17:19,168 --> 00:17:20,876
Yes, but barely.

253
00:17:22,540 --> 00:17:23,809
Akira-kun.

254
00:17:25,269 --> 00:17:26,324
Yes?

255
00:17:28,950 --> 00:17:29,920
(Club Application)

256
00:17:29,940 --> 00:17:32,678
Would you like to join the swimming club?

257
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:36,989
Sakuma-sensei...

258
00:17:38,227 --> 00:17:40,940
helped pull me up to the light.

259
00:17:47,220 --> 00:17:48,367
Sensei.

260
00:17:51,473 --> 00:17:52,503
Well...

261
00:17:54,492 --> 00:17:55,508
I...

262
00:18:02,186 --> 00:18:03,829
What should I do?

263
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:05,718
What's the matter?

264
00:18:07,170 --> 00:18:09,555
Shin. You're here.

265
00:18:12,150 --> 00:18:14,293
Have you met Sakuma-sensei?

266
00:18:15,720 --> 00:18:17,797
Yes, I met him.

267
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:21,560
