269
00:18:27,150 --> 00:18:28,320
Sensei.

270
00:18:32,348 --> 00:18:33,458
Well...

271
00:18:34,730 --> 00:18:35,759
I...

272
00:18:37,305 --> 00:18:38,337
like...

273
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:43,320
I like...

274
00:18:43,730 --> 00:18:44,760
