00:19:06,810 --> 00:19:10,590
- I like...
- You like...

286
00:19:10,610 --> 00:19:11,770
I know.

287
00:19:11,940 --> 00:19:13,420
Swimming club.

288
00:19:14,854 --> 00:19:18,540
Actually, I'd like to ask you
about that as well.

289
00:19:18,846 --> 00:19:19,914
Akira-kun.

290
00:19:20,560 --> 00:19:22,950
Would you like to join the swimming club?

291
00:19:25,150 --> 00:19:26,120
What?

292
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:27,850
As the swimming club coach?

293
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:30,070
Yes.

294
00:19:32,266 --> 00:19:33,656
Did you say yes?

295
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:35,540
Yes.

296
00:19:37,239 --> 00:19:39,699
I thought you were to going to
settle things with him.

297
00:19:40,170 --> 00:19:43,970
It seems like an important period
as the tournament is near.

298
00:19:43,990 --> 00:19:46,460
He insisted that I should help him.

299
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:48,610
It can't be helped.

300
00:19:51,725 --> 00:19:54,695
So you're happy that he asked you for help.

301
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,086
Let alone settling things with him.

302
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:59,365
You came back
without telling him how you feel.

303
00:19:59,389 --> 00:20:00,606
Am I right?

304
00:20:00,630 --> 00:20:01,934
It can't be helped.

305
00:20:02,390 --> 00:20:04,930
But my past and being a coach
are two different things.

306
00:20:04,930 --> 00:20:06,610
What about sensei?

307
00:20:06,890 --> 00:20:08,274
Shut up already.

308
00:20:08,298 --> 00:20:10,276
I can't understand myself either.

309
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,144
When you're an adult,

310
00:20:12,168 --> 00:20:14,640
there are things you can't decide
whether it's black or white.

311
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:18,250
Oh, right.

312
00:20:19,682 --> 00:20:22,462
I'm washing my bed sheet.

313
00:20:26,148 --> 00:20:28,388
It smells so good.

314
00:20:28,890 --> 00:20:31,230
Here, you can try sniffing it.

315
00:20:31,470 --> 00:20:32,732
It smells so nice.

316
00:20:53,910 --> 00:20:55,300
You really can't stay still.

317
00:20:55,650 --> 00:20:57,140
Are you really an adult?

318
00:20:59,038 --> 00:21:00,171
Sorry.

319
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:15,800
No, no, no.

320
00:21:15,820 --> 00:21:16,976
Not like this.

321
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,440
You can't do this.

322
00:21:21,070 --> 00:21:22,230
You're right.

323
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:24,050
It smells so nice.

324
00:21:26,350 --> 00:21:27,353
Hey.

325
00:21:27,377 --> 00:21:28,587
Stay still.

326
00:21:29,168 --> 00:21:31,708
I'm just sniffing the linen.

327
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:33,820
What?

328
00:21:34,759 --> 00:21:36,968
Don't sniff it like this.

329
00:21:48,062 --> 00:21:49,074
You rascal.

330
00:21:49,220 --> 00:21:50,290
Stop it.

331
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:52,830
I'm just feeling the sheet.

332
00:21:57,670 --> 00:21:58,800
Please.

333
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:00,430
Please stop.

334
00:22:01,820 --> 00:22:04,070
No, don't go further.

335
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,491
What's with that scream?

336
00:22:12,762 --> 00:22:15,420
Thanks to you, now I have to wash it again.

337
00:22:15,505 --> 00:22:17,675
Shin, you silly punk.

338
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:19,305
You crazy, handsome punk.

339
00:22:20,180 --> 00:22:21,679
I'm sorry, Minato-san.

340
00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:23,296
Can I borrow it?

341
00:22:24,260 --> 00:22:25,310
Come on.

342
00:22:33,630 --> 00:22:34,765
I'll be waiting.

343
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,380
Make sure you settle things with him.

344
00:22:40,702 --> 00:22:41,936
I know.

345
00:22:42,566 --> 00:22:44,286
Even the toughest of bedsheets,

346
00:22:44,607 --> 00:22:46,770
can be taken care of, over at
Minato's Laundromat.

347
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:55,710
Yaho.

348
00:22:55,730 --> 00:22:56,624
(Sakuma Store)

349
00:22:56,649 --> 00:22:58,772
So you're back.

350
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,374
Asuka.

351
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:05,730
Being wrapped in gentle and soft touch...

352
00:23:07,390 --> 00:23:08,420
Katsuki.

353
00:23:12,530 --> 00:23:15,083
I need to talk to you about something.

354
00:23:16,928 --> 00:23:20,158
Is definitely a bright morning welcome.

355
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:27,600
Welcome.

356
00:23:32,770 --> 00:23:34,500
It's been a while, Akira-kun.

357
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:37,700
Saki.

358
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:40,990
Please continue to support us next week.

359
00:24:44,870 --> 00:24:46,510
(Next Episode)
Can you give me some advice?

360
00:24:46,535 --> 00:24:47,675
(New love rival)
What are you doing?

361
00:24:47,710 --> 00:24:49,040
(New love rival)
What is it you want to talk about?

362
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:50,789
(The meeting of the past and future)
I see, you still can't figure

363
00:24:50,813 --> 00:24:52,096
what's on one's mind.

364
00:24:52,121 --> 00:24:54,451
I hope I get to see Shuu-sensei tomorrow.

365
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:57,350
What's the reason
you don't want to leave your hometown?

366
00:24:57,380 --> 00:24:59,750
(This drama is fictional)
Please tell me the truth.
